casebody.head_matter:
Tobias O. REED, petitioner,
v.
VIRGINIA.
No. 17-5402.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 28, 2018.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Virginia. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Supreme Court of Virginia for further consideration in light of Carpenter v. United States, 585 U.S. ----, 138 S.Ct. 2206, --- L.E.2d ---- (2018).
